<%- include('partials/header') %>

<!-- Mobile Navigation -->
<nav class="mobile-nav">
  <a href="/" class="mobile-nav-brand">
    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
    <span>SecureVault</span>
  </a>
  <button class="hamburger" id="hamburger" aria-label="Toggle menu">
    <span></span>
    <span></span>
    <span></span>
  </button>
  <div class="mobile-nav-menu" id="mobile-nav-menu">
    <a href="#features">See How It Works</a>
    <a href="#take-a-look">Take a Look</a>
    <a href="/login">Login</a>
    <a href="/register" class="btn-mobile-register">Get Started</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<main id="main-content">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero-board">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <div class="grid-pattern"></div>
      <div class="glow glow-1"></div>
      <div class="glow glow-2"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-badge-board">
          <span class="pulse-dot"></span>
          Live Demo
        </div>
        <h1 class="hero-heading">
          <span class="brand-name">SecureVault</span>
          <span class="brand-tagline">Built for developers who care about security</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-text">
          I built this authentication system to learn full-stack development and
          demonstrate production-ready security patterns. It's been used by friends
          and side projects — now I'm sharing it with you.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-ctas">
          <a href="/register" class="btn-board-primary">
            <span>Try it out</span>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
              <path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#features" class="btn-board-secondary">
            See how it works
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-metrics">
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-num">JWT</span>
            <span class="metric-label">Auth</span>
          </div>
          <div class="metric-divider"></div>
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-num">bcrypt</span>
            <span class="metric-label">Hashing</span>
          </div>
          <div class="metric-divider"></div>
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-num">Supabase</span>
            <span class="metric-label">Database</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Journey Section -->
  <section class="story-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="story-content" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="story-label">The journey</div>
        <h2 class="story-title">From Passport.js to Supabase</h2>
        <p class="story-text">
          I started building auth with <strong>Passport.js</strong> and express sessions — the classic
          approach. It worked locally, but when I tried deploying to <strong>Vercel</strong>, sessions
          kept breaking. Serverless functions don't store session data between requests.
        </p>
        <p class="story-text">
          That's when I discovered <strong>JWT tokens</strong>. Instead of storing user sessions on the server,
          the server sends the user a signed token. Every request includes that token, and the server
          just verifies it. No memory needed. No session store needed.
        </p>
        <p class="story-text">
          Then I moved from local PostgreSQL to <strong>Supabase</strong> — a cloud backend that handles
          authentication AND gives me a PostgreSQL database. It's like having a auth service built-in.
          Now the app can deploy anywhere, scale to infinity, and costs almost nothing to run.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features -->
  <section class="features-board" id="features">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="features-header" data-aos="fade-up">
        <span class="features-label">What's under the hood</span>
        <h2 class="features-title">What the app actually does</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card-board" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="feature-icon-board">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Supabase Auth</h3>
          <p>Cloud-based authentication with built-in user management. Handles signup, login, logout, and password reset out of the box.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card-board" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="150">
          <div class="feature-icon-board">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/>
              <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/>
              <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>JWT Tokens</h3>
          <p>Stateless authentication with JSON Web Tokens. 24-hour expiration stored in httpOnly cookies. No server session memory needed.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card-board" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
          <div class="feature-icon-board">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>bcrypt Hashing</h3>
          <p>Passwords hashed with 10 salt rounds. Even if the database leaks, passwords can't be reversed. Each hash is unique even for same password.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card-board" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="250">
          <div class="feature-icon-board">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Rate Limiting</h3>
          <p>5 login attempts per 15 minutes per IP. Protects against brute force attacks while staying usable for real users.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card-board" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
          <div class="feature-icon-board">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>SQL Injection Protection</h3>
          <p>Parameterized queries for all database operations. User input never goes directly into SQL strings.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card-board" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="350">
          <div class="feature-icon-board">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Vercel Deployment</h3>
          <p>Serverless-ready architecture. Auto-scales to handle any traffic. Global CDN for fast load times worldwide.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Demo Preview -->
  <section class="demo-board" id="take-a-look">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="demo-header" data-aos="fade-up">
        <span class="demo-label">Take a look</span>
        <h2 class="demo-title">The full user journey</h2>
        <p class="demo-subtitle">From creating an account to viewing your protected secrets.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- App Flow Visualization -->
      <div class="app-flow" data-aos="fade-up">

        <!-- Register Box -->
        <div class="flow-box">
          <div class="flow-label">Step 1: Register</div>
          <div class="app-card">
            <div class="app-card-header">
              <i class="fas fa-user-plus text-gold"></i>
              <span>Create Account</span>
            </div>
            <div class="app-card-body">
              <div class="app-field">
                <label><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Email</label>
                <input type="text" value="you@example.com" disabled>
              </div>
              <div class="app-field">
                <label><i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Password</label>
                <input type="password" value="••••••••" disabled>
              </div>
              <button class="app-btn app-btn-gold">Create Account</button>
            </div>
            <div class="app-card-footer">
              <span>Already have one? <a href="#">Login</a></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Arrow 1 -->
        <div class="flow-arrow">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <!-- Login Box -->
        <div class="flow-box">
          <div class="flow-label">Step 2: Login</div>
          <div class="app-card">
            <div class="app-card-header">
              <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt text-accent-flow"></i>
              <span>Welcome Back</span>
            </div>
            <div class="app-card-body">
              <div class="app-field">
                <label><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Email</label>
                <input type="text" value="you@example.com" disabled>
              </div>
              <div class="app-field">
                <label><i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Password</label>
                <input type="password" value="••••••••" disabled>
              </div>
              <button class="app-btn app-btn-accent">Login</button>
            </div>
            <div class="app-card-footer">
              <span>Don't have an account? <a href="#">Create one</a></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Arrow 2 -->
        <div class="flow-arrow">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <!-- Secrets Box -->
        <div class="flow-box">
          <div class="flow-label">Step 3: View Secrets</div>
          <div class="app-card app-card-secrets">
            <div class="app-card-header-secrets">
              <i class="fas fa-shield-check text-accent-flow"></i>
              <span>Access Granted</span>
              <span class="jwt-badge">JWT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="app-card-body-secrets">
              <div class="secret-preview">
                <i class="fas fa-user-secret"></i>
                <p>My secret recipe for chocolate chip cookies...</p>
                <span>Dec 15, 2025</span>
              </div>
              <div class="secret-preview">
                <i class="fas fa-user-secret"></i>
                <p>API keys for the production server...</p>
                <span>Dec 10, 2025</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="app-card-footer-secrets">
              <button class="app-btn-small app-btn-dark">Logout</button>
              <button class="app-btn-small app-btn-accent">Submit New</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <p class="flow-note" data-aos="fade-up">
        Each step is protected — users can only see their own secrets. The JWT token in your cookie proves who you are.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tech Stack -->
  <section class="tech-board">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="tech-header" data-aos="fade-up">
        <span class="tech-label">The tools I used</span>
        <h2 class="tech-title">Built with modern stuff</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-tags">
        <span class="tech-tag" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">Node.js</span>
        <span class="tech-tag" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="150">Express</span>
        <span class="tech-tag" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">PostgreSQL</span>
        <span class="tech-tag" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="250">JWT</span>
        <span class="tech-tag" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">bcrypt</span>
        <span class="tech-tag" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="350">EJS</span>
        <span class="tech-tag" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">Vercel</span>
        <span class="tech-tag" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="450">Supabase</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-board">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-box" data-aos="zoom-in">
        <h2>Want to try it?</h2>
        <p>Create an account and see the whole thing in action. No strings attached.</p>
        <div class="cta-actions">
          <a href="/register" class="btn-cta-board">
            Start for free
          </a>
          <a href="/" class="btn-cta-outline">
            Go back home
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<style>
/* ============================================
   Human-Touched Demo Page Styles
   ============================================ */

:root {
  --hb-bg: #0c0e14;
  --hb-bg-alt: #131820;
  --hb-bg-card: #1a1f2b;
  --hb-accent: #22c55e;
  --hb-accent-dim: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15);
  --hb-text: #f1f5f9;
  --hb-text-muted: #94a3b8;
  --hb-border: #2d3548;
  --hb-glow: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);
}

*, *::before, *::after {
  box-sizing: border-box;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

.container {
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 1.5rem;
}

/* Mobile Navigation */
.mobile-nav {
  display: none;
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  z-index: 1000;
  background: rgba(12, 14, 20, 0.95);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hb-border);
  padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
}

.mobile-nav-brand {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--hb-text);
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  text-decoration: none;
}

.mobile-nav-brand:hover {
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.mobile-nav-brand i {
  color: var(--hb-accent);
}

.hamburger {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 5px;
  width: 40px;
  height: 40px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  border: 1px solid var(--hb-border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
  padding: 8px;
}

.hamburger span {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--hb-text);
  border-radius: 2px;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.hamburger.active span:nth-child(1) {
  transform: rotate(45deg) translate(5px, 5px);
}

.hamburger.active span:nth-child(2) {
  opacity: 0;
}

.hamburger.active span:nth-child(3) {
  transform: rotate(-45deg) translate(5px, -5px);
}

.mobile-nav-menu {
  position: absolute;
  top: 100%;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  background: rgba(12, 14, 20, 0.98);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hb-border);
  display: none;
  flex-direction: column;
  padding: 1rem;
}

.mobile-nav-menu.active {
  display: flex;
}

.mobile-nav-menu a {
  color: var(--hb-text);
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: 0.9rem 0.5rem;
  font-size: 1rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hb-border);
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.mobile-nav-menu a:hover {
  background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1);
  color: var(--hb-accent);
  padding-left: 1rem;
}

.mobile-nav-menu a:last-of-type {
  border-bottom: none;
}

.btn-mobile-register {
  background: var(--hb-accent);
  color: #000 !important;
  text-align: center;
  border-radius: 0.5rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
  border: none !important;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .mobile-nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-board {
    padding-top: 5rem;
  }
}

/* Hero */
.hero-board {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  padding: 5rem 0;
}

.hero-bg {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: var(--hb-bg);
}

.grid-pattern {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 60px 60px;
}

.glow {
  position: absolute;
  width: 600px;
  height: 600px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  filter: blur(120px);
  opacity: 0.4;
}

.glow-1 {
  background: var(--hb-accent);
  top: -200px;
  right: -100px;
}

.glow-2 {
  background: #8b5cf6;
  bottom: -200px;
  left: -100px;
}

.hero-inner {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  max-width: 680px;
}

.hero-badge-board {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  background: var(--hb-accent-dim);
  border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);
  color: var(--hb-accent);
  padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
  border-radius: 2rem;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.pulse-dot {
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;
  background: var(--hb-accent);
  border-radius: 50%;
  animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
  50% { opacity: 0.4; }
}

.hero-heading {
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.brand-name {
  display: block;
  font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--hb-text);
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  line-height: 1.1;
}

.brand-tagline {
  display: block;
  font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.75rem);
  color: var(--hb-accent);
  font-weight: 400;
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
}

.hero-text {
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  color: var(--hb-text-muted);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  max-width: 540px;
}

.hero-ctas {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.btn-board-primary {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  background: var(--hb-accent);
  color: #000;
  padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem;
  border-radius: 0.5rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.btn-board-primary:hover {
  background: #16a34a;
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.btn-board-secondary {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem;
  color: var(--hb-text);
  font-weight: 500;
  text-decoration: none;
  border: 1px solid var(--hb-border);
  border-radius: 0.5rem;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.btn-board-secondary:hover {
  border-color: var(--hb-accent);
  color: var(--hb-accent);
}

.hero-metrics {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

.metric {
  text-align: left;
}

.metric-num {
  display: block;
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--hb-text);
}

.metric-label {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: var(--hb-text-muted);
}

.metric-divider {
  width: 1px;
  height: 30px;
  background: var(--hb-border);
}

/* Story Section */
.story-section {
  padding: 5rem 0;
  background: var(--hb-bg-alt);
}

.story-content {
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
}

.story-label {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  color: var(--hb-accent);
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.story-title {
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--hb-text);
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}

.story-text {
  font-size: 1.0625rem;
  color: var(--hb-text-muted);
  line-height: 1.75;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

/* Features */
.features-board {
  padding: 5rem 0;
  background: var(--hb-bg);
}

.features-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
}

.features-label {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  color: var(--hb-accent);
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.features-title {
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--hb-text);
}

.features-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

.feature-card-board {
  background: var(--hb-bg-card);
  border: 1px solid var(--hb-border);
  border-radius: 0.75rem;
  padding: 1.75rem;
  transition: all 0.25s ease;
}

.feature-card-board:hover {
  border-color: var(--hb-accent);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.feature-icon-board {
  width: 44px;
  height: 44px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  background: var(--hb-accent-dim);
  border-radius: 0.5rem;
  color: var(--hb-accent);
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}

.feature-card-board h3 {
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--hb-text);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.feature-card-board p {
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  color: var(--hb-text-muted);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* Demo Section */
.demo-board {
  padding: 5rem 0;
  background: var(--hb-bg-alt);
}

.demo-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.demo-label {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  color: var(--hb-accent);
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
